 an entire sleeve of fig newtons' l4d2 scripts
 ==============================================================

These are configuration files and scripts for playing Left 4 Dead 2 by Valve Software, Inc. Left 2 Dead 2 is a trademark of Valve Software.

* Directory structure

/ahk    autohotkey scripts that can be run in tandem with l4d2
/cfg    in-game configuration files
/npp    notepad++ syntax highlighting for source based configuration files

